title: sponge服务器后台报错初始化时检测到未注册的世界如何解决
author: Never_s
txt_content:
报错内容：attempt made to initialize dimension d 2 which isn't registered,falling back to overworld
如题 后台一直被这个刷屏，很难受

replies.author: a26605483
replies.txt_content:
config\sponge\global.conf
文件里修改
    # Add stack traces to dev logging
      log-stacktraces=true
为
     # Add stack traces to dev logging
        log-stacktraces=false
解决问题。

replies.author: Never_s
replies.txt_content:
